{"tha-ap439:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap439:0.2":"Ekaviharivagga ","tha-ap439:0.3":"Ambatakadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap439:1.1":"“Vipine buddham disvana, ","tha-ap439:1.2":"sayambhum aparajitam; ","tha-ap439:1.3":"Ambatakam gahetvana, ","tha-ap439:1.4":"sayambhussa adasaham. ","tha-ap439:2.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap439:2.2":"yam phalamadadim tada; ","tha-ap439:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap439:2.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap439:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap439:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap439:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap439:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap439:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap439:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap439:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap439:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap439:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap439:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ambatakadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap439:7.1":"Ambatakadayakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}